凯文科斯特纳在戛纳电影节上为激情项目“地平线”起立鼓掌https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-costner-in-tears-during-cannes-stand-ovation-for-passion-project-horizo​​n-3757679?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kevin-costner-戛纳电影节期间为激情项目地平线起立鼓掌热泪盈眶Sam WarnerMon, 20 May 2024 10:16:54 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3757679 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯文·科斯特纳" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位明星已经首映了他期待已久的电影传奇</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-costner-in-tears-during-cannes-standing-ovation-for-passion-project-horizon-3757679">凯文·科斯特纳 (Kevin Costner) 在戛纳电影节为激情项目“地平线”起立鼓掌时泪流满面的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯文·科斯特纳" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kevin-Costner-at-Cannes-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-costner">凯文·科斯特纳</a>在他的新片<em>《地平线：美国传奇》</em>获得全场起立鼓掌后，明显情绪激动。</p><p>这部被描述为由两部分组成的西部片，一直是演员和导演长期热衷的项目，于昨天（5 月 19 日）在戛纳电影节上首映。</p><p>据报道，放映结束后，科斯特纳获得了长达七分钟的起立鼓掌，视频显示这位演员泪流满面。</p><p> <em>《地平线》</em>已经制作了 35 年，以美国内战期间为背景，重点关注美国西部的扩张。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7KXlynIbxs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34