b-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> BABYMONSTER于4月发行的《BABYMONS7ER》标志着他们的首次回归，主打曲是《Sheesh》。这张唱片也标志着乐队与 Ahyeon 的首张专辑，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yg-entertainment-trainee-ahyeon-no-longer-debut-babymonster-health-reasons-3539693">由于未具体说明的健康原因，Ahyeon 去年不得不缺席乐队的正式首演</a>。</p><p> 《BABYMONS7ER》也标志着乐队继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-new-single-stuck-in-the-middle-3564422">二月份发行独立单曲《Stuck In The Middle》</a>之后今年第二次发行音乐。该乐队于 2023 年底凭借<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-swing-for-the-big-leagues-on-debut-single-batter-up-3549426">单曲“Batter Up”</a>首次亮相。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yg-entertainment-plans-new-babymonster-treasure-music-this-fall-3757647">YG Entertainment 宣布今年秋季推出新 BABYMONSTER、TREASURE 音乐的计划</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
