f="https://www.nme.com/artists/metro-boomin">《地铁》</a>中的“今年早些时候”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-video-for-kendrick-lamars-new-song-humble-2030984">“谦卑”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-takes-aim-at-drake-and-j-cole-on-metro-boomins-like-that-fuck-sneak-dissin-first-person-shooter-3608327">之类的</a>角色开始，该歌曲于2017年到达，并他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-talks-taylor-swift-collaboration-2170944">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）2015年的曲目“ Bad Blood”上的经文。</a></p><p>按照“那样”，德雷克用两条曲目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-taunts-kendrick-lamar-says-he-has-nothing-to-drop-in-response-to-push-ups-diss-track-3620086">“俯卧撑”</a>和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-taunts-kendrick-lamar-again-with-a-i-2pac-and-snoop-dogg-on-taylor-made-freestyle-3719747">泰勒制造的自由泳</a>”向后射击。加拿大说唱歌手在使用AI效仿<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tupac-Shakur">图帕克·沙库尔（Tupac Shakur</a> ）的人声之后，降落在热水中，导致已故的说唱歌手的财产<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tupac-shakurs-estate-threatens-legal-action-against-drake-over-diss-track-using-ai-generated-vocals-3750354">威胁法律诉讼</a>。随后，他从流媒体上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-removes-diss-track-using-ai-generated-tupac-vocals-after-estate-threatens-lawsuit-3751219">删除了曲目</a>。</p><p>然后，拉马尔（Lamar）将于5月1日以“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-drake-diss-track-euphoria-features-sample-of-reversed-richard-pryor-line-from-the-wiz-3752511">Euphoria</a> ”的回应，第二天很快就以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-drops-another-brutal-drake-diss-track-616-in-la-3753398">“ 6:16”的身份在洛杉矶</a>进行回应。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-responds-to-kendrick-lamar-diss-with-family-matters-lamar-drops-meet-the-grahams-an-hour-later-3753494">然后，两人在一个小时的一个小时内放下了新的Diss曲目，</a> Drake在Lamar拍手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-responds-to-kendrick-lamar-diss-with-family-matters-lamar-drops-meet-the-grahams-an-hour-later-3753494">“ Meet the Grahams”</a>之前释放了“家庭事务”。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-claims-he-fed-kendrick-lamar-false-intel-on-new-diss-the-heart-part-6-3753644">德雷克（Drake）声称他在新的Diss“心脏第6部分”上喂了Lamar False Intel</a> ，但这首歌并不受到粉丝的欢迎 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-the-heart-part-6-has-over-1million-dislikes-on-youtube-kendrick-lamar-feud-3754786">最近在YouTube上超过了100万不喜欢的人</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">在这里</a>查看一个仇恨的完整时间表。</p><p>至于Eilish，她最近的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">由<em>NME</em>发表了四星级评论</a>，并被描述为“大胆，出色且更加明亮”。</p><p> “比利（Billie）以创造性地和个人的个人渴望进入这个过程：&#39;打我辛苦而柔软&#39;仍然是独一无二的，这是一个奇异才能进入年轻成年的肖像，探索了她的古怪，并经历了情感上的刺激和（有时）灾难。追逐激情或坠入爱河的是。</p><p> “在为自己写一张专辑时，她制作的会比以前做的任何事情都更难引起共鸣。”</p><p>在上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-new-album-hit-me-hard-and-soft-3614974">宣布专辑的详细信息</a>之后不久，这位“坏人”歌手继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">宣布一场2024  -  2025年世界巡回演唱会</a>，以支持LP  - 将于今年秋天开始。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处购买我们的门票</a>，并在这里购买<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国门票</a>。</p><p>自发行以来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-and-finneas-have-never-ever-ever-loved-something-more-than-new-album-hit-me-hard-and-soft-3757252">她和兄弟/合作者Finneas都对专辑打开了有关专辑的开放，并说他们“从未喜欢过更多的东西”</a> ，并且已经显示出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-how-billie-eilishs-blue-lyrics-relate-to-every-song-on-hit-me-hard-and-soft-3757332">&#39;Blue&#39;的歌词都引用了完整的LP曲目列表</a>。</p><p>邮报<a